1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,500
Codex asks when it knows it is uncertain.

2
00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:11,000
PromptTripwire detects when reasonable Codex runs silently disagree.

3
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:17,500
Three independent read-only planning probes expose a material alternative.

4
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:23,500
The source label and support counts explain why this question needs a human.

5
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:29,500
Only the human selects the bounded local implementation.

6
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:36,000
The answer becomes an immutable execution contract with explicit change scope and checks.

7
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Dependencies, network, remote writes, deploy, release, and external effects stay blocked.

8
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:49,000
This v0.1.12 source preview uses a deterministic fixture and is not live execution evidence.
